  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00001",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张良武装佩剑上。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00002",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "张良"
      ],
      "text": "堂堂好男子，最好沙场死。死只一回勿浪死，不报国仇誓不止！",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00003",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张良"
      ],
      "text": "唉，秦始皇吓！你并吞六国，安坐江山，也就罢了！还要造长城，筑阿房，焚书坑儒。百姓们说了你半个暴字，就立刻性命难保！",
      "text_length": 57
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00004",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张良拔剑怒视。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00005",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张良"
      ],
      "text": "我张良若不设法除你，也没有人心天理了！",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00006",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张良收剑。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00007",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张良"
      ],
      "text": "前日见了苍海公，可敬他不顾自己身体，情愿为百姓除害，我不免助他一臂之力，一为百姓除害，二为韩国报仇！好不快活也！",
      "text_length": 56
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00008",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张良走圆场。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00009",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "张良"
      ],
      "text": "可恨那秦嬴政昏荒无道，他本是西戎种混乱中朝。灭六国篡江山位登大宝，变封建为郡县起祸根苗。把公产当私财行同强盗，把人民当奴隶滥逞英豪。筑长城一万里到处骚扰，阿房宫三百里内藏娇娆。焚了书坑了儒种种不道，若民间有私议性命难逃。他还想传万世",
      "text_length": 116
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00010",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "张良"
      ],
      "text": "天命当保，他还想成神仙快乐逍遥。只恨我穷书生身微力小，空怀着报仇志昼夜心焦。望国民起义师恭行天讨，到如今还不见草泽英豪。好让那虎狼秦多行凶暴，只苦了众百姓受尽煎熬。我想把好乾坤重新构造，我想把专制君万剐千刀。本是我祖国仇理应当报，恨不能学专诸刺杀王僚！",
      "text_length": 126
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00011",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人内嚷。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00012",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "秦皇帝来到，还不早躲么！",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00013",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张良作惊。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00014",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "张良"
      ],
      "text": "猛听得众百姓纷纷嚷道，待鄙人走向前细问根苗。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00015",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张良"
      ],
      "text": "诸位请了！所嚷何事？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00016",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "秦皇帝又东游泰山，昨日路过阳武，就此驻驿了。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00017",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张良作惊喜。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00018",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "笑",
      "speakers": [
        "张良"
      ],
      "text": "呵哈哈哈哈！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00019",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张良"
      ],
      "text": "我正想锄刈此贼，无法可施。不料他竟自先来送死，真令我好欢喜也！",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00020",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "张良"
      ],
      "text": "我正想起义兵诛锄无道，谁料他入罗网插翅难逃。我不免访苍海把细情说了，替祖国报公仇就在今朝！",
      "text_length": 45
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00021",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张良走圆场。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00022",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张良"
      ],
      "text": "来此已是苍海公家，不免上前叩门。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00023",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张良叩门。苍海公上。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00024",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "苍海公"
      ],
      "text": "眼中黑白要分明，天谴魔君杀不平。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00025",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "苍海公"
      ],
      "text": "外面何人叩门？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00026",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张良"
      ],
      "text": "我是张良。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00027",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "苍海公开门。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00028",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "苍海公"
      ],
      "text": "原来是子房兄！请里面谈话。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00029",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张良、苍海公同入。苍海公关门。张良、苍海公分坐。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00030",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张良"
      ],
      "text": "苍海公，",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00031",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "苍海公"
      ],
      "text": "子房兄。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00032",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张良"
      ],
      "text": "我已打听明白，那暴君明日从博浪沙经过，请公就在此地行事如何？",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00033",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "苍海公"
      ],
      "text": "子房兄见教极是，但是子房兄须要躲避才是啊。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00034",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "苍海公"
      ],
      "text": "尊一声张公子且宽怀抱，你赶紧整行装事先奔逃。但愿我此一去大功成了，且免得事不成遗累英豪。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00035",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张良执苍海公手，起立。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00036",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "张良"
      ],
      "text": "尊一声苍海公你见识太小，自古道共患难与子同胞。你心中休得要自寻烦恼，我与你早已订生死之交。",
      "text_length": 45
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00037",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "苍海公"
      ],
      "text": "公子差矣！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00038",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "苍海公"
      ],
      "text": "我非是将公子有心取笑，我要想留一个恢复根苗。要知道我此去凶多吉少，为什么要同去枉死一遭。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00039",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张良"
      ],
      "text": "既然如此，即当遵命了！苍海公在上，受我一拜！",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00040",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "苍海公"
      ],
      "text": "我也有一拜！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00041",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "苍海公"
      ],
      "text": "苍海公在尘埃将身拜倒，生辞别张子房盖世英豪。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00042",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张良起立执手。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00043",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "苍海公"
      ],
      "text": "倘若是我此去事机不妙，逃走了这魔道世外逍遥。还望你施妙计将仇来报，莫把这弥天恨抛在九霄。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00044",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张良"
      ],
      "text": "勇士前往，但请放心。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00045",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "张良"
      ],
      "text": "秦始皇灭六国冤仇非小，为天下除此贼天日昭昭。我若是昧良心忍辱不报，我死在九泉下万劫难逃。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00046",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "苍海公"
      ],
      "text": "既是如此，公子就请起程。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00047",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张良"
      ],
      "text": "遵命了！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00048",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张良更衣。家院上，牵马。张良揖别。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00049",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "张良"
      ],
      "text": "辞别了苍海公把路行！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00050",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张良上马，哭。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00051",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "苍海公"
      ],
      "text": "子房好男子，为何作此儿女之态？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00052",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "张良"
      ],
      "text": "等候了苍海公成就大功！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00053",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张良催马，下。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00054",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "笑",
      "speakers": [
        "苍海公"
      ],
      "text": "呵哈哈哈哈！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00055",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "苍海公"
      ],
      "text": "听一声秦嬴政位离大宝，我这里霎时间怨气全消。我想他一年年淫乐怠傲，扰害得众百姓啼哭嚎啕。想是他恶满盈天算已到，今日里要在我锥下……",
      "text_length": 65
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00056",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "苍海公观锥。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00057",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "苍海公"
      ],
      "text": "狗命难逃！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00058",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "苍海公收铁锥，下。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00059",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四太监、四御林军同上。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00060",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "咦咦咦咦！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00061",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "秦始皇戴王帽、穿黄龙蟒袍上。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00062",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "秦始皇"
      ],
      "text": "竹帛烟消，兵气销。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00063",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "秦始皇坐。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00064",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "秦始皇"
      ],
      "text": "法律由专断，威权种祸胎。生不访家贼，死上断头台。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00065",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦始皇"
      ],
      "text": "朕，秦始皇。因前日百姓不服，私下议论纷纷，所以朕特颁一条极严法律：倘若有人，私下议论，立刻问斩，以免后患。又观东南王气正盛，所以命驾东巡，察看那里的民情，这正是为君的难啊！",
      "text_length": 86
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00066",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "秦始皇"
      ],
      "text": "百姓们不知是朕即国家，朕立意除净那民党萌芽。有爪牙和心腹护卫孤家，又何怕有刺客在博浪沙。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00067",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦始皇"
      ],
      "text": "唉！话虽如此，但是古人说得好，有备无患，方是这个主意呵！",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00068",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "秦始皇"
      ],
      "text": "叫一声内侍臣，",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00069",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "太监"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00070",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "秦始皇"
      ],
      "text": "安排副车，张姓冠李姓戴莫要喧哗。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00071",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "喳！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00072",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00073",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "苍海公穿短衣、腰插铁锥上。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00074",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "苍海公"
      ],
      "text": "准备窝弓擒猛虎，安排香饵钓鳌鱼。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00075",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "苍海公"
      ],
      "text": "来此已是博浪沙，远听得车马声响，不免登高一望。（苍海公登高探望。四太监、四御林军同上，车夫推假秦始皇同上。苍海公跳下，拔锥打杀二太监，打死假秦始皇。四御林军同拔刀相打，苍海公被擒。众人同下。）",
      "text_length": 96
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00076",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四太监引秦始皇同上。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00077",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "秦始皇"
      ],
      "text": "若非巧计安排定，已作黄泉新鬼魂。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00078",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "秦始皇里位坐。二御林军同上。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00079",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "二御林军"
      ],
      "text": "启奏万岁：刺客拿着了！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00080",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦始皇"
      ],
      "text": "绑上来！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00081",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "二御林军"
      ],
      "text": "绑上殿来！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00082",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "喳！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00083",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "二御林军押苍海公背绑同上。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00084",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "苍海公"
      ],
      "text": "悲哉秦人真虎狼，欺侮六国囚侯王。亦知兴废古来有，但恨不见秦先亡。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00085",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "二御林军同跪。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00086",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 86,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "二御林军"
      ],
      "text": "刺客解到。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00087",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 87,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦始皇"
      ],
      "text": "大胆刺客，你受何人主使，胆敢前来行刺？从实招来，免尔一死。",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00088",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 88,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "苍海公"
      ],
      "text": "尔这暴君，人人想食尔肉！我为民除害，有何人主使？有也不向尔说！你杀我一人，也难安安稳稳，长保你金銮殿上这把金交椅！",
      "text_length": 57
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00089",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 89,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "秦始皇气。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00090",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 90,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦始皇"
      ],
      "text": "好毒骂啊！啊哈，好毒骂呀！御林军与朕剁作肉泥骨酱！",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00091",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 91,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "御林军拔刀，苍海公撞柱自死。御林军举刀乱砍。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00092",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 92,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "御林军"
      ],
      "text": "刺客死了！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00093",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 93,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦始皇"
      ],
      "text": "这人是一夫之勇，暗中必有主使。左右与朕大搜十日！",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00094",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 94,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "御林军"
      ],
      "text": "遵旨！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00095",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 95,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦始皇"
      ],
      "text": "斩草除根，方免后患！呵哈哈哈哈！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00096",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 96,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00097",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 97,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张良急上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00098",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 98,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张良"
      ],
      "text": "闻得苍海公已死，暴君命人各处搜杀主使之人，这、这、这、这便如何是好？",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00099",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 99,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张良低头想。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00100",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 100,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张良"
      ],
      "text": "哈哈有了！我有故人项伯，在下邳居住，不免到他家躲避便了！唉！苍海公呵！苍海公！我误你的命了！",
      "text_length": 46
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00101",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 101,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张良向空拜。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00102",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 102,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "起驾。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00103",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 103,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张良"
      ],
      "text": "这暴、暴、暴、暴……",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00104",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 104,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "喳！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005104_e00105",
      "play_id": "70005104",
      "scene_id": "70005104_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 105,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张良慌忙逃下。",
      "text_length": 7
    }
  ],
  "roles_inferred": true
}